Package: unbound-pihole-profile
Architecture: all
Depends: unbound (>= 1.25.1-1~bookworm1), unbound (<< 1.25.2~), ${misc:Depends}
Description: conservative Unbound profile for a local Pi-hole resolver
 Installs a loopback-only recursive resolver profile on port 5335 and socket
 buffer sysctls. It deliberately does not modify Pi-hole or host networking.
